      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Complete List: TWL Dictionary</h2>

      <p>In the TWL (Tournament Word List, used in North America), exactly two words end in the letter Q. Both are valid plays in any sanctioned tournament.</p>

